{
  "stem": "21648.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's cool.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Days or nights, we didn't know [INAUDIBLE] this day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know when it's day and night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we, more or less, we saw a little light.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Complain?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The children?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, they took straw, and they was doing from straw some-- what did they know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know only one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- when before we was on the barn on top, so through the straw, they saw the chicken running around and the children play.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they used to say the two girls, why are the chicken running around free?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why can't we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why can't we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Please, let us go down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they'll hurt us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're not afraid to be hurt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let us go, mommy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let me go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My little one was too smart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every day, she said, mother, let me go for a half an hour, a little bit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just want to run back and forth, and I come back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was terrible hard to keep them quiet and to keep them happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I guess when you're scared, you accept everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The time was not long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The days wasn't too long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You-- you was only thinking, I'll survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll survive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And every day came the guy and told us they just took [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They find so many Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they took them to Rovne, and they kill them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They find so many Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They took them to Rovne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the good news what he used to bring us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, one day, he came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, the war is finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when he said that, [SOBBING] I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOBBING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left the children with them-- I, my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
